vote.title: An ordinance approving Dallas-Fort Worth International Airport Board Resolution No. 2020-09-198, adopted on September 3, 2020 for the purpose of amending Appendix I of the Code of Rules and Regulations of the Dallas-Fort Worth International Airport Board, as follows:  Appendix I is amended to include proposed new streets, 20th Avenue (N & S), 22nd Avenue (N & S), 34th Street (E & W) and 35th Street (E & W) at the Southwest Campus development site on Dallas-Fort Worth International Airport property - Financing: No cost consideration to the City
